OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy periods to start the
OL,6,Fday, some rain possible across the
OL,7,FPennines but remaining dry for most
OL,8,Fplaces. Sunny spells developing during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon with a few showers
OL,10,Flikely. Temperatures remaining above
OL,11,Faverage for the time of year.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny remaining showers fading
OL,14,Fduring the evening, then turning dry
OL,15,Fand settled overnight with the wind
OL,16,Feasing. Staying mild for most places
OL,17,Falthough a little cooler in rural
OL,18,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
