OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloud quickly thickens as it
OL,6,Fturns to a rather grey and wet day for
OL,7,Fmost places. Heavy outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fpossible in the afternoon and evening.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FWet
OL,11,Fand windy weather continues as bands
OL,12,Fof rain move through followed by
OL,13,Fbrighter but showery interludes.
OL,14,FTemperatures dropping down to normal
OL,15,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
